fields.name: Date
fields.description: {"value":"","fieldValueType":"dateAndTime"}

fields.name: ReportedOn
fields.description: {"value":"Reported On refers to the number of new confirmed positive CoVID-19 cases reported on the specified date.","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: ReportedCum
fields.description: {"value":"Reported Cumulative refers to the cumulative number of positive CoVID-19 cases by the specified date. ","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: Deceased
fields.description: {"value":"The number of individuals reported deceased from CoVID-19 on specified date.","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: Recovered
fields.description: {"value":"The number of individuals confirmed recovered from CoVID-19 on specified date.","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: Hospitalized
fields.description: {"value":"The cumulative number of individuals who have ever been hospitalized for CoVID-19 symptoms by the specified date. ","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: ICU
fields.description: {"value":"The cumulative number of individuals ever in the Intensive Care Unit (ICU) on the specified date, due to CoVID-19 related symptoms.","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: Vent
fields.description: {"value":"The cumulative number of individuals on ventilators on the specified date, due to CoVID-19 related symptoms.","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: StillIll
fields.description: {"value":"The number of individuals who currently report CoVID-19 related symptoms by the specified date.","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: PosPatients
fields.description: {"value":"The total number of patients who have tested positive for CoVID-19 on the specified date.","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: PUIPatients
fields.description: {"value":"The number of Persons Under Investigation (PUI) due to contact with an individual confirmed positive for CoVID-19 on the specified date.","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: DeathsCum
fields.description: {"value":"The cumulative number of CoVID-19 related deaths on the specified date. ","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: COVIDnICU
fields.description: {"value":"The total number of CoVID-19 patients in Intensive Care Units (ICU) on the specified date. ","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: COVIDonVent
fields.description: {"value":"The total number of ventilators in use by CoVID-19 patients on the specified date. ","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: TotalVents
fields.description: {"value":"The total number of ventilators in use on the specified date. ","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: AvailVent
fields.description: {"value":"Total number of ventilators not currently in use, and available to treat patients on specified date. ","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: TotalStaffedBeds
fields.description: {"value":"The total number of hospital beds that are licensed and for which staff is on hand to attend on the specified date. ","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}

fields.name: AvailStaffedBeds
fields.description: {"value":"The total number of unoccupied hospital beds that are licensed and physically available for which staff is on hand to attend on the specified date.","fieldValueType":"countOrAmount"}
